4 HR____ CELEBRATING REVEREND JEFFERY BLACK ON THE OCCASION OF
5 HIS 10TH PASTORAL ANNIVERSARY.
6
7 WHEREAS, with great pride and special pleasure, we
8 highly honor Reverend Jeffery Black for his 10 years of
9 pastoral service of Mt. Moriah Baptist Church Cardiff in
10 Adamsville, Alabama; and
11 WHEREAS, Reverend Black graduated from Wenonah High
12 School in 1995 and answered his call to ministry early,
13 being licensed in 1994; he was later ordained in 2002,
14 solidifying his commitment to serving God and his community;
15 and
16 WHEREAS, he pursued his theological education with
17 fervor, graduating from the Birmingham Easonian Baptist
18 Bible College and culminating in 2012 with his Bachelor of
19 Arts in Pastoral Theology; and
20 WHEREAS, his academic achievements prove that he is
21 dedicated to deepening his understanding of the Word and
22 enhancing his ministry skills; and
23 WHEREAS, in addition to his pastoral duties, Reverend
24 Black works at Arrington Funeral Home, where his compassion
25 and empathy provide solace to grieving families; his dual
26 roles in ministry and funeral services reflect his
27 commitment to offering comfort and guidance during life's
28 most challenging moments; and
Page 1

most challenging moments; and
HR185 INTRODUCED
29 WHEREAS, despite the personal loss of both his
30 parents and the passing of his beloved wife, Reverend Black
31 continues to inspire those around him with his unwavering
32 faith and perseverance; his life and ministry are a
33 testament to the strength and grace that come from a deep
34 relationship with God; and
35 WHEREAS, Reverend Black is a beacon of hope and a
36 pillar of the community, dedicated to spreading the love of
37 Christ and supporting those in need; his journey is marked
38 by resilience, compassion, and dedication to his calling;
39 now therefore,
40 BE IT RESOLVED BY THE HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES OF THE
41 LEGISLATURE OF ALABAMA, That we extend heartfelt
42 congratulations to Reverend Jeffery Black on the occasion of
43 his 10th Pastoral Anniversary, and this resolution is
44 offered to him with deepest admiration and appreciation,
45 along with sincere best wishes for all future endeavors.
